FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772037602
OL,3,CZelenskyy says Putin has 'not broken'
OL,4,CUkrainians four years after invasion
OL,6,FZelenskyy said on social media:
OL,7,F"Looking back at the beginning of the
OL,8,Finvasion and reflecting on today, we
OL,9,Fhave every right to say: We have
OL,10,Fdefended our independence, we have not
OL,11,Flost our statehood.
OL,13,F"He has not broken Ukrainians; he has
OL,14,Fnot won this war."
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
