FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772037602
OL,3,CZelenskyy says Putin has 'not broken'
OL,4,CUkrainians four years after invasion
OL,6,FHe added that Russian President
OL,7,FVladimir Putin has "not achieved his
OL,8,Fgoals".
OL,10,FAs the war of attrition enters its
OL,11,Ffifth year, peace negotiations are
OL,12,Fstuck on what happens to the Donbas
OL,13,Fregion and the terms of a postwar
OL,14,Fsecurity arrangement that Kyiv is
OL,15,Fdemanding to deter any future Russian
OL,16,Finvasion.
OL,26,@oD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772037602
OL,3,CZelenskyy says Putin has 'not broken'
OL,4,CUkrainians four years after invasion
OL,6,FAt a makeshift memorial in Kyiv's
OL,7,Fcentral square, Zelenskyy said he
OL,8,Fwould like US President Donald Trump
OL,9,Fto visit and witness for himself
OL,10,FUkrainian suffering.
OL,12,FZelenskyy said: "Only then can one
OL,13,Ftruly understand what this war is
OL,14,Freally about."
OL,16,FHe said he expected a fresh round of
OL,17,FUS-brokered talks with Russia within
OL,18,Fthe next ten days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
